# LEGO WeDo device driver

menuconfig WEDO
	tristate "LEGO WeDo support"
	depends on USB
	select LEGOEV3_LEGO_SENSORS
	select LEGO_DC_MOTORS
	select LEGO_SERVO_MOTORS
	help
	  Say Y here if you want to connect a LEGO WeDo hub to your USB
	  ports.

	  To compile this driver as a module, choose M here: the
	  module will be called wedo.
